name: Procedure Customer Report
query:
select E.name,I.item_group, E.patient,E.patient_name,E.owner,E.encounter_date,E.patient_sex,E.inpatient_record, E.Practitioner,E.visit_department,
E.invoiced, E.branch,P.creation,P.parent,P.invoiced,P.procedure,P.owner
from `tabPatient Encounter` E ,`tabProcedure Prescription` P, tabItem I
where E.name = P.parent
and I.item_code = P.procedure
